  "general_provisions": "This bill modifies income tax provisions.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>amends the corporate franchise and income tax rates; <hr><ltbullet>amends the individual income tax rate;<hr><ltbullet>creates an addition for domestic research and experimental expenditures that a taxpayer fully deducts on the federal tax return for a taxable year; and<hr><ltbullet>authorizes a taxpayer that adds back domestic research and experimental expenditures to subtract those expenditures according to an amortization schedule on the state tax return.",
